{
  "_comment": [
    "Zentrale Pi-Konfiguration für die hotsport-access Drehkreuze.",
    "",
    "Workflow:",
    "  1. Diese Datei editieren (neuen Pi-Eintrag ergänzen oder ändern).",
    "  2. git commit && git push",
    "  3. Auf dem Pi: install.sh aufrufen, Pi-ID auswählen, fertig.",
    "",
    "Was hier rein gehört (kein Geheimnis):",
    "  - Hub-URL                          (LAN-IP, optional für Status-Dashboard)",
    "  - Binarytec-API Base-URL + TLS     (LAN-IP, nicht-secret)",
    "  - Pro Pi: pi_id, name, location, reader_mode, inout, interface_id,",
    "    GPIO-Pins, Reader-Devicepfad/Kamera-Index",
    "",
    "Was NICHT hier rein gehört (Repo ist public):",
    "  - api.bearer_token (Binarytec)     -> install.sh fragt ihn interaktiv ab",
    "  - hub.pi_token                     -> install.sh fragt ihn interaktiv ab"
  ],

  "hub": {
    "base_url": "http://192.168.0.86:8765"
  },

  "api": {
    "base_url": "https://192.168.251.50:444",
    "verify_tls": false,
    "connect_timeout_seconds": 1.0,
    "request_timeout_seconds": 2.0
  },

  "defaults": {
    "reader_mode": "keyboard",
    "reader_device_path": "/dev/input/event0",
    "reader_camera_index": 0,
    "relay_pin": 24,
    "relay_pulse_seconds": 1.0,
    "buzzer_pin": 23
  },

  "pis": [
    {
      "pi_id": "hotsport-pi-01",
      "name": "Eingang Nord",
      "location": "hotsport",
      "reader_mode": "keyboard",
      "inout": "in",
      "interface_id": "101"
    },
    {
      "pi_id": "hotsport-pi-02",
      "name": "Eingang Süd",
      "location": "hotsport",
      "reader_mode": "keyboard",
      "inout": "in",
      "interface_id": "102"
    },
    {
      "pi_id": "hotsport-pi-03",
      "name": "Ausgang Nord",
      "location": "hotsport",
      "reader_mode": "keyboard",
      "inout": "out",
      "interface_id": "103"
    }
  ]
}
